<br>
We got him on the second charge that night, and I think a couple key elements were a couple more wizards and a MUCH better strategy! Honestly I think the strategy is something where I should have known better, and it woulda even saved the 10 minutes of bind rushing last week..<br>
<br>
I was VERY much at the point that I wanted to call it a night as well, Thanks so much everyone for believing we could take him and for being patient with me as I wrestled with my doubts!<br>
<br>
I'm dead tired, I haven't even openned the logs yet, but I think I hit the hay at 4 AM! The first of the fire giants was respawning, but we got the loot distributed and everyone out before it affected anyone.<br>
<br>
Drops, right, I was really happy because now Honeysong is 1 piece and 1 triggered spawn from her epic. =) <br>
<br>
Red Dragon Scale: Honeysong<br>
Selo's Drum of the March: Fragoth<br>
Cloak of Flames: Phread<br>
Gauntlets of Fiery Might: Lenian<br>
Gauntlets of Fiery Might: Rezzar<br>
Prayer of Life: Sinrok<br>
<br>
